      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<label> <span>2. Energy performance improvement and monitoring </span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_1\">Use energy monitoring and management hardware and\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsoftware <span class=\"checkmark\" id=\"2_1\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tTo understand how to change something, it is essential to assess it first. List of energy\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmanagement software for organization may vary from open source to commercial fully\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsupported products. <br>Reference - <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"http://www.capterra.com/energy-management-software/\">Energy management software</a>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2\">Enable PC energy saving functions <span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_2\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPurchase low power CPU's, omplement thin clients <br>Thin client computing provides\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tusers with the same interface, applications, and performance as a desktop based computer but\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthrough a slim lined desktop device. Be cause the thin client's performance is driven by a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tserver instead of a local processor, there can be significant power savings when used in a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlarge environment. But thin clients are not always an appropriate solution - although they\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlead to cheaper clients with less energy consumption, they also lead to more communications\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tand data centre applications and potentially higher energy consumption in the data centre.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThis balance needs to be assessed for your own particular circumstance.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2_1\">Switch off unused devices completely <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2_1\">Shut down PC equipment after hours, or use remote\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tmonitoring software solutions to do so</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Turn off peripherals, or set them to stand-by mode respectively <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Switch on/off WiFi Access Points <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_2\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_2_2\">Power management software can automate switch off\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tactivities <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_3\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_2_2\">You can set up a 'dimming and switch off' option on\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tyour PC by adjusting your OS settings. Dimming and switching off occurs automatically after\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\ta certain period (e.g. 5 minutes) when the PC has been idle. You can start saving energy by\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlooking for the power options in your OS. Computers and monitors account for half the\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\telectricity used in an office and energy is being wasted every day, even by \"energy saving\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thardware. For example, in a company with 200 PCs, turning off all the computers and monitors\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tevery night and at weekends would save &pound;12,000 a year.</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4\">Integration assessment into management system (Green IT\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tofficer) <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_4\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCarbon emissions can be calculated from the energy consumption of your ICT department's\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinfrastructure, which is then useful in planning and prioritising projects.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 1 - Establish a measurement team. Creating a team to measure the carbon\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tfootprint is important. Asking each team member to carry out the measurement activity\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trelevant to their responsibilities is key to measure correctly and to spark sustainable\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthinking.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 2 - Define a measurement timeline. It sounds basic, but putting a timeline in\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tplace will ensure that this activity, which may not be viewed as business critical, is\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcompleted in a timely fashion.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Step 3 - Undertake and collate measurement activities. The <a\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thref=\"./Calculate.jsp\">CALCULATE</a> section shows and explains how to make estimations on\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thow to convert energy consumption of ICT equipment into a carbon footprint.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4_1\">Use multifunction devices<span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_4\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4_1\">Consolidate equipment and use MultiFunction Devices\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t(printers, copiers, scanners)</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4_2\">Adjust monitor's brightness <span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_4\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4_2\">Also, consider replacing CRT monitors with LCD</div>\n");
