      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4_4\">Printing centralization <span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_4\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4_4\">When considering imaging equipment such as\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tprinters, scanners, faxes, copiers a ratio of 10:1 is considered best practice i.e. ten\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\temployees to 1 device. To improve the ratio in your organisation replace individual\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tprinters, scanners etc. with multi-functional devices and also review the location of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tequipment. By placing printers in shared areas, rather than in team areas it is possible to\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\treduce the number of printers that are required. This also has the added benefi t of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdiscouraging wasteful printing if employees have to walk a bit further to collect the\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tprinting. Utilise print authentication solutions - prints are only output upon user\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tauthentication at the printer</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_4_5\">Optimize cooling in server rooms<span class=\"checkmark\"\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tname=\"2_4\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_4_5\">ICT equipment in a server room such as servers,\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tstorage- and network equipment cause considerable heat. Cooling helps to ensure the\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\treliability of this equipment. Optimize cooling by optimizing the air current. Make sure\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tthat cold air is lost or blocked as little as possible.</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_5\">Use of alternative energy from renewable sources <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_5\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_5\">Electricity generation from renewable sources\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsignificantly reduces the carbon footprint of electricity. On-site electricity generation\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsystems using solar, wind, geothermal or biomass energy can be set up in order to supply ICT\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tequipment with low-carbon electricity. On-site generation: The renewable energy source is\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tproduced on site, e.g. by building wind turbines or by setting up solar PVs on the roof (in\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\turban areas) or around the facility (in rural areas).</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_2_5_1\">Install energy-efficient rectifiers <span\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tclass=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_5\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_2_5_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tInstalling newer energy-efficient rectifiers and selecting ICT equipment functioning with DC\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcurrent may reduce energy losses due to energy conversion. The efficiency gains of using DC\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\thave both a direct benefit (fewer power conversions) and indirect benefit (less generation\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tof heat). There are several environmental benefits of reducing energy losses. Benefits of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tenergy losses reductions are expected in the following domains:\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Reduction of energy waste, thanks to the reduction of large quantities of\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnon-productive power consumed by the infrastructure;</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Reduction of waste heat, thanks to a better management of the activity of the\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tservers and the reduction of electricity voltage conversions of UPS. In addition, the\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tquantity of heat to be cooled by the air conditioner will decrease, thereby decreasing\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tnon-productive power consumption;</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>CO2 emissions are expected to decrease due to less power consumed.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>ICT equipment functioning with DC current may reduce energy losses due to energy\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tconversion <span class=\"checkmark\" name=\"2_5\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t</div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t<div class=\"form-radio-buttons\" id=\"V3\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<label> <span>3. Energy aware networks engineering adherence </span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"flip\" id=\"flip_3_1\">Network infrastructure deploying intelligent switches,\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPower over Ethernet <span class=\"checkmark\" id=\"3_1\"></span></li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_3_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWith various networking equipment available on market deployment of managed switches can get\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcapabilities such as cable diagnostics, prioritization of traffic using default QoS\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsettings, Energy savings capabilities using EEE (Energy Efficient Ethernet) and even PoE\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t(Power Over Ethernet). <br>Reference - <a\n");
