      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tid=\"3_3\"></span>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t</li> </label>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_3_3\">Dynamic rerouting (nodes and links switch off, traffic\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\tredistribution, etc.) and protection technology (filters, sorry servers, etc.) can result in\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsignificant energy savings by controlling the traffic in a dynamic manner. Optimising data\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\trouting and transmission characteristics (e.g. changing of traffic path, adjusting\n");
