      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel\" id=\"panel_4_2_1\">\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe main principles behind any successful behaviour change programme apply to changing\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbehaviours around ICT.\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ol>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Information - enabling people to make informed decisions. â¢ Deliver information in\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tan engaging and positive way.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Maximise the message conveyed with interactivity and discussion.</li>\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>Link individual actions to the bigger picture to personalise the issue and help\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpeople to recognise the power of collective will.</li>\n");
